# Incident 03 - Systemd Service Fails Due to Wrong Path

## Symptoms

- Service repeatedly restarting
- localhost:8080 unreachable
- curl failed

## Investigation

Checked:

- systemctl status troubleshoot
- service file
- project structure

Found:

- Nested troubleshooting-lab directory
- ExecStart pointing to incorrect path

## Root Cause

Service referenced a path that no longer existed after moving project files.

## Resolution

- Flattened repository structure
- Updated WorkingDirectory
- Updated ExecStart
- Reloaded systemd
- Restarted service

## Verification

- Service status active (running)
- curl localhost:8080 successful

